            Durio, Jackie

            Page Navigation

            • About Me
            • 2024-2025 Supplies
            • Summer Reading 2024

            Phone: 281-327-7978

            Email: jackie.durio@fortbendisd.gov

            Degrees and Certifications:

            I am certified in ELA, Social Studies, and Reading. I also have a certification in GT and ESL.

            Mrs. Jackie Durio

            Hello, Welcome to my page.  This is my seventh year at Clements.  I have taught for thirty-six years in various districts,  and I am certified in English-Language Arts, and Social Studies.  I also hold certifications in Gifted Education and English as a Second Language.    I am originally from New Mexico and moved to Texas in 2002. While in Texas, I have lived in Denton, Galveston, Seabrook, and now Sugar Land. I have three daughters, four grandchildren, and three dogs.   I truly love teaching and the opportunity to help students reach their potential.  

            Please check the other pages for school supplies and summer reading choices. 

            I look forward to working with you and your child. 

            • Teacher Tutorial Schedule

              My tutorials are every Tuesday and Thursday afternoon from 3:00-3:30.  Additional tutoring may be available by appointment. You can reach me via e-mail jackie.durio@fortbendisd.gov  Please make sure you add something in the subject line, or it will not be delivered.
